{"tid":2453682,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［紅店提示］片仔癀 係由中共持有57%","createTime":"2021-03-19T15:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T05:03:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2ecd7d80536ae53e5aa053c3696633c266edbe","tid":2453682,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:23:03.000Z","msg":"上巿公司<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.zzpzh.com/index.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zzpzh.com%2Findex.aspx&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=96d086ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.zzpzh.com/index.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n黨資佔57%<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yyyZFcb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyyZFcb.png&h=160dd52a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cbN7O5x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcbN7O5x.png&h=1a9110c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.zzpzh.com/uploadfiles/2020/08/202008211742134213.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zzpzh.com%2Fuploadfiles%2F2020%2F08%2F202008211742134213.pdf&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=62727f57\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.zzpzh.com/uploadfiles/2020/08/202008211742134213.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"7eb2b47d9f20ce35bf2052d23d697e4695c02cf9","tid":2453682,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"最近仲喺cctvb落廣告<br />\n<br />\n最近TVB廣告時段成日有個女人喺度大叫，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一嚟煩，二嚟膠，三嚟&hellip;條女參加過「一戴一露」嘅？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ep9Fn7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fep9Fn7U.jpg&h=c8f1925b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃子桐，原名黃曉婉，未入行先奶共，做緊學生嗰陣已經參加一戴一露交流團，再上TVB吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSRo5Gz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSRo5Gz.jpg&h=7276d73d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一戴一露小姐，文匯報都有你嘅身影喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">來自香港大學的學生黃曉婉發言表示，冀籍此活動瞭解祖國繁榮</span></span></strong>，並探清自身未來發展方向。她的發言贏得許昆林副市長和歐陽曉晴主席的讚許。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dSSWGfd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdSSWGfd.png&h=14cceda6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黃同學，知唔知一戴一露最成功輸出嘅係咩嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GXhLzG7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGXhLzG7.png&h=7942b5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年選党姐選唔到，但都碌咗TVB做茄里啡，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">反送中運動過後，毅然與TVB簽訂經理人合約</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5GqhqPe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5GqhqPe.jpg&h=1c1fb21b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年之前的確有好多粉紅港豬，但2020年都未醒，真係幫你唔落，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">請派嬲畀黃子桐嘅廣告商<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">🚫 片仔癀牙膏(捷成藥業) 🚫</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PZH.HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPZH.HK%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=68bfba78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PZH.HK/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/3klZa7oTB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpili.app%2Fpg%2F3klZa7oTB&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=dfde8423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pili.app/pg/3klZa7oTB</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ep9Fn7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fep9Fn7U.jpg&h=c8f1925b&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n[吖你老母]片仔癀牙膏條女可唔可以靜少少呀仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2453480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2453480</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c26fc7b604e62461d1d8634c4fb8d92c4dacf29a","tid":2453682,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T01:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236a9bb6679e9c5f4bc0955fdb82460973773ea0","tid":2453682,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03824de2186ad10998143a61fce6bbe8232a331","tid":2453682,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2ef16dac92c99fa8fbec56f30002b227d2d275","tid":2453682,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:34:52.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1b76767ad7be564e2b7f3e5a94f5129802b8c9b7","tid":2453682,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T23:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9852464970a6eec31c1813e6fc514eaca47526","tid":2453682,"uid":255717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T00:22:08.000Z","msg":"支味牙膏"},{"pid":"2d447c7a6a287939e1cdb9c4719090011b13d07b","tid":2453682,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}